{"type":"message","id":"761ce2fa","parentId":"413dea72","timestamp":"2026-04-15T14:03:53.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0e7DjLF3uGOQldCBREYiMIiZ|fc_0738c49d7888ee550169df9abe0cf4819096e07a0c852e8467","name":"message","arguments":{"accountId":"3b92905a192c-im-bot","action":"send","activityName":"","activityState":"","activityType":"custom","activityUrl":"","after":"","appliedTags":[],"around":"","asDocument":false,"asVoice":false,"authorId":"","authorIds":[],"autoArchiveMin":60,"before":"","bestEffort":false,"buffer":"","caption":"","categoryId":"","channel":"openclaw-weixin","channelId":"","channelIds":[],"chatId":"","clearParent":false,"contentType":"","deleteDays":0,"desc":"","dryRun":false,"durationMin":0,"effect":"","effectId":"","emoji":"","emojiName":"","endTime":"","eventName":"","eventType":"","filePath":"","filename":"","forceDocument":false,"fromMe":false,"gatewayToken":"","gatewayUrl":"","gifPlayback":false,"groupId":"","guildId":"","image":"","includeArchived":false,"includeMembers":false,"kind":"","limit":0,"location":"","media":"","memberId":"","memberIdType":"open_id","members":false,"message":"找到原因了。\n\n飞书主控这个对话之所以“不受控制”，不是飞书问题，是 **OpenClaw 把飞书私聊会话按固定 peer 复用** 了。当前配置里 `session.dmScope = per-account-channel-peer`，所以同一个飞书 bot + 同一个人私聊，会一直落到同一条历史会话里，不会因为你说“新会话”就自动开新上下文。\n\n我已经确认主控的飞书私聊会话确实存在，而且是被系统持续复用的那条。\n\n如果你要我继续，我下一步会直接在本机找可用的会话管理命令，尝试把这条主控飞书私聊会话从 OpenClaw 会话存储里删掉，这样飞书下次发消息就会自动生成新会话。\n\n你回我一句：`继续删旧会话`\n我就直接动手。","messageId":"","message_id":"","mimeType":"","name":"","nsfw":false,"openId":"","pageSize":0,"pageToken":"","parentId":"","participant":"","path":"","pollDurationHours":0,"pollId":"","pollMulti":false,"pollOption":[],"pollOptionId":"","pollOptionIds":[],"pollOptionIndex":0,"pollOptionIndexes":[],"pollQuestion":"","position":0,"query":"","quoteText":"","rateLimitPerUser":0,"reason":"","remove":false,"replyTo":"","roleId":"","roleIds":[],"scope":"","silent":false,"startTime":"","status":"online","