{"type":"message","id":"91e2a7f5","parentId":"a8a0b47e","timestamp":"2026-04-15T14:09:22.301Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e6iACbK7LqfEjvQicvGmPh5C|fc_002e8262d88bc5c00169df9c0cab788194ab4bcbbaa8594b0c","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.12 (1c0672b) — I don't have opinions about tabs vs spaces. I have opinions about everything else.\n\nUsage: openclaw sessions [options] [command]\n\nList stored conversation sessions\n\nOptions:\n  --active <minutes>  Only show sessions updated within the past N minutes\n  --agent <id>        Agent id to inspect (default: configured default agent)\n  --all-agents        Aggregate sessions across all configured agents (default:\n                      false)\n  -h, --help          Display help for command\n  --json              Output as JSON (default: false)\n  --store <path>      Path to session store (default: resolved from config)\n  --verbose           Verbose logging (default: false)\n\nCommands:\n  cleanup             Run session-store maintenance now\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw sessions\n    List all sessions.\n  openclaw sessions --agent work\n    List sessions for one agent.\n  openclaw sessions --all-agents\n    Aggregate sessions across agents.\n  openclaw sessions --active 120\n    Only last 2 hours.\n  openclaw sessions --json\n    Machine-readable output.\n  openclaw sessions --store ./tmp/sessions.json\n    Use a specific session store.\n\nShows token usage per session when the agent reports it; set agents.defaults.contextTokens to cap the window and show %.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/sessions\nOllama could not be reached at http://127.0.0.1:11434.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"plaid-breeze","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Ollama could not be reached at http://127.0.0.1:11434.\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.12 (1c0672b) — I don't have opinions about tabs vs spaces. I have opinions about everything else.\n\nUsage: openclaw sessions [options] [command]\n\nList stored conversation sessions\n\nOptions:\n  --active <minutes>  Only show sessions updated within the past N minutes\n  --agent <id>        Agent id to inspect (default: configured default agent)\n  --all-agents        Aggregate sessions across all configured agents (default:\n                      false)\n  -h, --help          Display help for command\n  --json              Output as JSON (default: false)\n  --store <path>      Path to session store (default: resolved from config)\n  --verbose           Verbose logging (default: false)\n\nCommands:\n  cleanup             Run session-store maintenance now\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw sessions\n    List all sessions.\n  openclaw sessions --agent work\n    List sessions for one agent.\n  openclaw sessions --all-agents\n    Aggregate sessions across agents.\n  openclaw sessions --active 120\n    Only last 2 hours.\n  openclaw sessions --json\n    Machine-readable output.\n  openclaw sessions --store ./tmp/sessions.json\n    Use a specific session store.\n\nShows token usage per session when the agent reports it; set agents.defaults.contextTokens to cap the window and show %.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/sessions\n\n","name":"openclaw sessions"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776262162297}}
